## 8. Prioritized Improvement Roadmap

### Phase 1 — Critical Fixes (1-2 days)
- [ ] **Fix duplicate routes** (`/student/grades`, `/admin`, `/admin/audit`)
- [ ] **Fix duplicate imports** (`ProfessorDashboard`, `StudentDashboard`)
- [ ] **Fix frontend API URLs** to match backend kebab-case routes
- [ ] **Fix sidebar dead links** (`/grades`, `/finance`, `/auditing`, `/student/payments`)
- [ ] **Fix [ErrorBoundary](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/pages/errors/ErrorBoundary.jsx#5-43)** env check (`import.meta.env.DEV`)

### Phase 2 — Security & Performance (3-5 days)
- [ ] **Add `React.lazy()` + `Suspense`** for all page routes
- [ ] **Add `AbortController`** to [useFetch](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/hooks/useFetch.js#4-36) hook
- [ ] **Fix [useFetch](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/hooks/useFetch.js#4-36) stale closure** bug
- [ ] **Wrap [logout](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/contexts/AuthContext.jsx#10-11)** in `useCallback`
- [ ] **Throttle [useIdleTimer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/hooks/useIdleTimer.js#5-58)** event listeners
- [ ] **Replace `window.location.href`** with React Router `useNavigate`

### Phase 3 — UX & Accessibility (5-7 days)
- [ ] **Add escape key + focus trap** to Modal
- [ ] **Add proper ARIA attributes** to Tables, Forms, and Toast
- [ ] **Add skip-to-content** link
- [ ] **Build real [DeanDashboard](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/routes/index.jsx#63-64)** page
- [ ] **Add responsive CSS** for admin, report, and cashier pages
- [ ] **Add consistent empty/error states** to all pages
- [ ] **Move [ProgramHeadDashboard](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/frontend/src/routes/index.jsx#64-143)** to its own file

### Phase 4 — Polish (2-3 days)
- [ ] **Centralize grades API** module
- [ ] **Add loading skeletons** to data-heavy pages
- [ ] **Add double-click/submit protection** on critical actions
- [ ] **Remove `console.log`** from demo page
